                    <a href="mailto:grahamtomori10@gmail.com" class="text-[#3B2F2F] underline">contactgrahamtomori@gmail.com</a>
                </p>

                <!-- Experience -->
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Experience</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 list-disc ml-6">
                        <li>
                            <strong>Glenridge Lawn Service — Entrepreneur</strong> (Summer 2021). Founded small business; video ads, yard work, landscaping.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>DECA Business Competition — Competitor</strong> (Winter 2022–2024). Advanced to provincials; honed business/marketing roleplay.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Niagara Games Soccer Dept — Volunteer</strong> (Summer 2022). Assisted at Youngs Sportsplex; engaged with athletes/coaches nationwide.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Clifton Niagara Group — Sales Associate</strong> (Spring 2023–2025). High-volume tourist sales; top performer; repeat seasonal
                            hire.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Now for Net Zero — Steering Committee</strong> (Fall 2024). Reviewed 60+ national grants ($25k max each); advised funding allocations.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>ARI Scholarship Recipient</strong> (Spring 2025). Fully funded trip to Austin, TX; seminars on philosophy, business, and life
                            approaches.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Education -->
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Education</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 list-disc ml-6">
                        <li><strong>Wheatley Montessori School</strong> (2009–2021). IB program; A+ average; ADHD research project & site.</li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Eden High School</strong> (2021–2025). Honor Roll; DECA; OFSAA medals (track, cross country); accelerated academics.
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Butler University</strong> (2025–Present). B.A. International Business; NCAA finalist (5000m/10,000m).</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Sports & Extracurricular -->
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Sports & Extracurricular</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 list-disc ml-6">
                        <li><strong>Edge Swimming Club</strong> (2022–2025). Early morning training; CPR/safety certified.</li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Edge Running Club</strong> (2022–2025). 2025 U18 Canadian national champions (team); fastest 3000m U18 Canada (2024). Recruited
                            by 75+ universities.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Awards & Hobbies -->
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Awards & Hobbies</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 list-disc ml-6">
                        <li>Grants/scholarships exceeding $250,000.</li>
                        <li>Ontario Power Generation award (solar research).</li>
